descriptionNullable:
The dataset contains images of 35 different breeds of snakes. The images have been scraped from Google Images. However the data collection was inspired from the Hackerearth Challenge: https://www.hackerearth.com/challenges/competitive/hackerearth-deep-learning-challenge-snake-breed-detection/

The Python script which I have used to scrape images is here: https://github.com/debadridtt/Scraping-Google-Images-using-Python
title: Identifying different Breeds of Snakes
subtitle: Snake Breed Classification
